":"2020-10-01T04:22:17.000Z","msg":"性關係而家如何？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"7年仲keep到，犀利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"其實我想三四日一次 但佢唔想 果時嘈左一輪"},{"pid":"8261e39c2e47e03a6618cb58266ab3e61f8ec7a4","tid":2224733,"uid":75232,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"用咩心態？<br />\n<br />\nGood question<br />\n<br />\n我同我老婆都算係一見鍾情嘅。識咗三日就傾咗次通宵電話，第二晚約食飯然後就一齊咗。拍咗五年半拖之後結婚，而家都差唔多結咗五年。<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣剩係想俾幸福呢個咁堅強嘅女仔，而家都係想繼續俾幸福呢個捱咗十六個鐘幫我生個女嘅老婆。<br />\n<br />\n另外，我知道我要搵個管得到我嘅女人做老婆，如果唔係嘅話啲錢一定左手嚟右手去。而我老婆就真係管得住我個人同埋啲錢，佢仲要之後做埋會計師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。簡稱我計劃成功，搵到個幫我儲到錢嘅好老婆。"},{"pid":"3d1fe02e5b42d10f4489d030417e34a35fbf2d43","tid":2224733,"uid":101845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abdd7bf7c95fcd3914aa48de3ed65e6ec13593ef","tid":2224733,"uid":245441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cffe64d6571384972015fa6286433dece0a65688","tid":2224733,"uid":101845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb653abe0718835a58d9d24a65c06ba776ae088a","tid":2224733,"uid":245441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"7年仲keep到，犀利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"其實我想三四日一次 但佢唔想 果時嘈左一輪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T07:26:49.000Z","msg":"點解唔想"},{"pid":"3c199a663e21239b47fd4d5a903c58a30c105fc0","tid":2224733,"uid":245441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d1fe02e5b42d10f4489d030417e34a35fbf2d43","tid":2224733,"uid":101845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abdd7bf7c95fcd3914aa48de3ed65e6ec13593ef","tid":2224733,"uid":245441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cffe64d6571384972015fa6286433dece0a65688","tid":2224733,"uid":101845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"7年仲keep到，犀利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"其實我想三四日一次 但佢唔想 果時嘈左一輪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T07:26:49.000Z","msg":"點解唔想"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T07:33:16.000Z","msg":"咁佢身體係幾奇怪<br />\n想要果星期會好濕<br />\n但另外果兩星期 就算睇av 都會好乾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我梗係想成日做啦"},{"pid":"22c3cbc45bb0f70c12d1f8c0a921c7acc94e3f5f","tid":2224733,"uid":19487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"嗰陣真係冇乜特別，佢話結咁咪結囉，同埋大家一齊咗已經好耐習慣晒"},{"pid":"e43e6e336320c4580edf3a1b6ec2507c31874db0","tid":2224733,"uid":19487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22c3cbc45bb0f70c12d1f8c0a921c7acc94e3f5f","tid":2224733,"uid":19487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"嗰陣真係冇乜特別，佢話結咁咪結囉，同埋大家一齊咗已經好耐習慣晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T07:37:43.000Z","msg":"拍咗10年先結"},{"pid":"b26f6e3edfac5fbdf21b2d3a5a6c1ad2187fc62d","tid":2224733,"uid":27568,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:30:33.000Z","msg":"唔好結婚<br />\n千祈唔好結婚<br />\n如果我唔係結左婚<br />\n我唔會喺呢度同你哋講呢一番說話<br />\n<br />\n同人相處好麻煩<br />\n淨係旅行都睇唔清一個人<br />\n要住埋D問題先出晒來<br />\n仲有對方父母<br />\n無品又唔識尊重人<br />\n老婆死都要生BB<br />\n又唔考慮自己無錢<br />\n係過去好多年都無工作果隻<br />\n又唔為BB著想<br />\n女人想生仔同男人咸濕一樣無理智"},{"pid":"f4737f6d8520f69295358f0e331e8874d6683d31","tid":2224733,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6365ae25a25e94078a5745a56ae6d2b0d8e9f6d","tid":2224733,"uid":38904,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.esdcdn.com/wow/attachment/201510/27/58654_1445956053VVu9.jpg?w=480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.esdcdn.com%2Fwow%2Fattachment%2F201510%2F27%2F58654_1445956053VVu9.jpg%3Fw%3D480&h=7ba41a84&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:37:46.000Z","msg":"用mma十字固鎖鳩老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06916ba800001029c7157e1724cd784f73aab5c3","tid":2224733,"uid":357936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:39:44.000Z","msg":"我爛命一條，怕咩？"},{"pid":"a44c97a9df76af671ff6dc91a33fe5628b850956","tid":2224733,"uid":31784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:56:02.000Z","msg":"講埋幾歲先比到建議你"}]}